subject: Fantasy Sports
Gambling
Regulation and Deregulation of Industry
lead_paragraph: A law firm hired by DraftKings found that although Ethan Haskell inadvertently released data about contestants’ lineups, he was unable to use that information to win money on the rival site FanDuel.
